data.description: Welcome Home! This beautiful 4 bedroom, 3 bath is immaculate. This house sits on almost 1.5 acres.  This house has all of the big city feels, while maintaining country isolation.  The details in this house are amazing, you have to come out and view it firsthand.  Wow your guest as your new home features multiple flex rooms, large living room, and plenty of natural lighting.  New appliances were just added and will stay! Your new yard is massive and is ready to host your next family gathering. The house comes equipped with a new zero turn mower that will convey with sell. Did we mention no HOA...YES, you read that right NO HOA! Schedule your private showing today.
